title: Angry Birds Star Wars 1.0 Android
description:
English

Description: Angry Birds is the new Star Wars game from Rovio's popular franchise based on the iconic Star Wars universe. The new version of the popular game turns angry birds characters in the saga and brings new skills to the birds so they can defeat the pigs - which are now the dark side of the force.

Get ready to experience great adventures in the universe! Angry Birds In Star Wars, Luke Skywalker becomes Red, Yellow turns Han Solo, Chewbacca appears as Big Brother and King Pig is Darth Vader. Altogether there are more than 30 different characters from Star Wars fan to put any defect.

The first challenge of the players will be on Tatooine, the planet where Obi-Wan Kenobi hides with baby Luke in the history of the saga. Then the players will have to face Darth Vader on the Death Star.
